text: Michael Peter (born 8 September 1968) is a German rower. He competed in the men's coxed pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:German male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Germany Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
